  "title": "Senior Electrical Engineer (Oil & Gas)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is from Oil and Gas industry, a local leading player. They are looking for a Senior Electrical Engineer for the next phase of their business. They are located in West.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Duties:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supervise and enhance the reliability of electrical equipment in the Gas Engine Generator (GEG) area.</li>\n  <li>Implement and maintain reliability programs and maintenance procedures for electrical systems.</li>\n  <li>Manage minor CAPEX electrical projects in line with company standards.</li>\n  <li>Investigate electrical failures to identify root causes and implement solutions.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with external stakeholders, including government agencies, on electrical matters.</li>\n  <li>Support major expansion projects from an electrical and operational perspective.</li>\n  <li>Work with Licensed Electrical Workers to ensure system integrity.</li>\n  <li>Participate in emergency response, with assigned roles and responsibilities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Bachelor’s Degree in Electrical Engineering or any relevant field.</li>\n  <li>Min 5 years’ experience in Oil &amp; Gas or Petrochemical industry</li>\n  <li>Experience in Electrical maintenance or design</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>\n<p><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p>\n<p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p>\n<p>EA License No: 19C9682</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
